        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Current roster visible: 5x more tryout inquiries</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Team had 2022 roster only. Updated to current roster prominently. Month 1: 5x more tryout signups. Current = active = join now.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Achievement history visible: 67% more credibility</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added championship history prominently. Month 1: 67% more serious players. History = winning = want to join.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Coach credentials visible: 53% more trust</p>
