              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added clear tryout details prominently. Month 1: 43% smoother registration. Clear = understand = sign up.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile team browsing: 87% check on phones</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Sports = mobile browsing. Non-responsive roster = skip this team. Mobile-optimized = view roster = tryout.</p>
