        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-blue-400 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Squarespace AI</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase">Sports Templates</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Team-focused templates designed. Roster grids showcase players elegantly. Schedule calendars built-in. Championship history displays beautifully.</p>
            </div>
