            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase">Performance</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">95+ PageSpeed. Optimized image delivery. CDN included. Fastest loading rosters.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase">Limitations</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Learning curve steep. Build time 2-3 days. Requires design decisions. Higher initial effort. No sports templates.</p>
            </div>
