              <p class="text-gray-700">Limited sports templates. Basic e-commerce. Younger platform. Template variety growing. Feature gaps vs. Squarespace.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Wix AI</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase">Ease of Setup</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">AI generates site in minutes. Sports templates included. Drag-and-drop roster builder. Quick schedule pages.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase">Features</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Booking system for tryouts. Event calendar for matches. Payment processing. Email marketing to players.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase">Mobile App</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Manage roster from phone. Update scores on-the-go. Tryout notifications instant. Schedule changes push alerts.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase">Limitations</p>
