          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">Webflow for custom league management. Build custom CMS for multiple teams, standings tables, schedule sync APIs. Squarespace works for single-team sites. Wix has multi-site management but performance suffers (70-75 PageSpeed). If you're managing 5+ teams with shared standings, player loans between teams, complex scheduling: Webflow. If you're one team with basic schedule: Squarespace. League management = custom build = Webflow wins.</p>
